headline.main: BRITISH GET PLANES AT A RECORD RATE; Deliveries of Air Equipment in Nine Months of 1941 Reached Total of $330,000,000

lead_paragraph: LOS ANGELES, Nov. 15 (AP) -- Delivery of warplanes and aeronautical equipment to Britain reached a record high of $330,000,000 in eight months of 1941, the Aeronautical Chamber of Commerce of America reported today.
abstract: Rept on Brit aircraft purchases and U S deliveries to Sept 1
